Trinity::

She was giggling as she held on to Archangles back.  She fired her 
tiny optic lazars at the trainers as best as she could.  She saw one 
bot and tried to turn her head around to fire at him.  She let go of 
his shoulder with one paw and turned.  Then her other paw slipped and 
she lost her balance.  She fell off his back and fell towards the 
ground. "MMMMEEEEEEOOOOOOOOWWWWWWWWWW!"
